📖 Surah Al-Ma‘un 

Surah: 107 – Al-Ma‘un
Ayat: 7
Nazool: Makki Surah

🔹Allah Ta‘ala is surah mein un logon ki pehchaan karwate hain jo deen ko jhutlate hain.
Deen ka matlab sirf namaz ya zahiri ibadat nahin, balki insaaniyat, khidmat aur ikhlaas bhi hai.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📌 Ayah-by-Ayah

✅Ayah 1–2

"Ara’aita alladhi yukazzibu biddin. Fadhalika alladhi yadu’ul-yateem."
➡️ "Kya tumne dekha us shakhs ko jo Deen ko jhutlata hai? Wohi hai jo yateem ko dhakka deta hai."

🔎 Tafseer:

➡️Jo aakhirat aur hisaab ka inkaar karta hai, uski zindagi mein zulm aur sakhti hoti hai.
➡️Aisa insaan yateem ki care karne ke bajaye unko zaleel karta hai.
➡️Islam mein yateem ki himayat karna imaan ki buniyad hai 
  (Hadith: Nabi ﷺ ne yateem ka sponsor banne walay ko Jannat mein apne qurbat ka waada diya).

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

✅Ayah 3

"Wala yahuddu ‘ala ta‘amil miskeen."
➡️ "Aur gareeb ko khilane par ubharta bhi nahi."

🔎 Tafseer:

➡️Yeh shakhs na khud madad karta hai aur na hi dusron ko motivate karta hai.
➡️Islam mein gareeb ki madad sirf ek optional act nahin, balki social responsibility hai.
➡️Allah yeh dikhate hain ke deen sirf ibadat nahi, insaaniyat aur social justice bhi hai.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

✅Ayah 4–5

"Fawailullil musalleen, alladhinahum ‘an salatihim sahoon."
➡️ "Tabahi hai un namazi logon ke liye, jo apni namazon mein ghaflat karte hain."

🔎 Tafseer:

➡️Yahan un namaziyon ki baat ho rahi hai jo namaz ko sirf ek show bana dete hain.
➡️Kabhi parhte hain, kabhi chhod dete hain, waqt ka khayal nahin karte, dil mein Allah ka zikr nahi hota.
➡️Namaz ka asal maqsad insan ko burai aur fahsh se rokna hai (Surah Ankabut 29:45).

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

✅Ayah 6

"Alladhinahum yura’oon."
➡️ "Jo riya karte hain."

🔎 Tafseer:

➡️Riya matlab logon ko dikhane ke liye amal karna.
➡️Yeh log sirf duniya mein izzat aur naam ke liye ibadat karte hain, nafrat se nahi balki Allah ki raza se doori ki wajah se.
➡️Hadith: Nabi ﷺ ne riya ko "chhoti shirk" kaha hai.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

✅Ayah 7

"Wa yamna‘oonal ma‘oon."
➡️ "Aur woh chhoti chhoti madad bhi rok dete hain."

🔎 Tafseer:

➡️Ma‘un ka matlab chhoti chhoti madad (jaise paani dena, bartan udhaar dena, roz marra ki chhoti cheezen).
➡️Yeh log itne kanjoos aur sakht dil hain ke chhoti si madad bhi nahi karte.
➡️Islam yeh sikhata hai ke chhoti si help bhi Allah ke nazdeek bohot qeemti hai.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌟 Lessons (Sabaq):

➡️Deen ka asal matlab sirf namaz aur ibadat nahi – balki social justice, khidmat aur insaaniyat bhi deen hai.
➡️Yateem aur gareeb ki care imaan ka bunyadi hissa hai.
➡️Namaz sirf ritual nahi, balki ikhlaas aur waqt par ada karna zaroori hai.
➡️Riya (show-off) amal ko barbad kar deti hai. Amal sirf Allah ke liye hon.
➡️Chhoti si madad bhi iman ka hissa hai – paani dena, salam karna, muskaan dena bhi sadqah hai.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌙 Reflection  (Sochne ka Sawaal):

👉 Kya meri ibadat sirf zahiri hai ya dil se hai?
👉 Kya main apni zindagi mein chhoti chhoti madad karne ki aadat rakhta hoon?
👉 Kya main yateem aur gareeb ki fikr karta hoon ya sirf apne kaam mein masroof rehta hoon?

